title: Strictly Come Dancing: the highlights and lowlights (Gleb put his shirt back on) from week four
text:
Strictly Come Dancing: the highlights and lowlights (Gleb put his shirt back on) from week four Strictly Come Dancing: the highlights and lowlights (Gleb put his shirt back on) from week four Share 
Strictly Come Dancing hasn’t been short of action, and it’s only week four. 
In a nutshell: Gleb Savchenko got fans TALKING (and drooling), Anton Du Beke SCORED a major victory, Pop star Paula Abdul was nearly upstaged by her dog… and much more. 
Here are the lowlights and highlights from the show: 
1. Highlight: Gleb took off his shirt and people went crazy 
— Sema Malik (@sema_malik_WL) October 17, 2015 *Swoons* Who knew that song was about Glebs hips! swivel your hips my way #Gleb . #Ridebag #GlebsHipsDontLie #scd pic.twitter.com/C4OPdSQybU
